FBIS4-41277 "drsov121_p_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia `Temporary' Trade Rules for Iranian Border Set `Temporary' Trade Rules for Iranian Border Set NC2206200894 Yerevan SNARK in English 1110 GMT 22 Jun 94 NC2206200894 Yerevan SNARK English BFN ["Temporary Rules of Armenia-Iran Border Trade"--SNARK headline] [Text] Yerevan, 22 June (SNARK) -- Armenian citizens were given the right for a tax-free export and import of goods into the trade zone at the Armenia-Iran border, for a total sum not exceeding $1,000. In the case the amount is surpassed, a tax is imposed on goods under the valid agreement. According to Armenian Government decision issued today, barter trade is also allowed in the zone.
